OL,3,CWildlife left covered in diesel after
OL,4,Coil spill in chalk stream
OL,6,FThousands of litres of oil have
OL,7,Fspilled into the environment and
OL,8,Fpolluted a rare chalk stream in
OL,9,FLondon, officials have said.
OL,11,FThe Environment Agency said an
OL,12,Festimated 4,000 litres of oil had
OL,13,Fspilled into surface water drains and
OL,14,Faffected the River Wandle, a once-
OL,15,Fheavily industrialised chalk stream
OL,16,Fthat has been revived and is now home
OL,17,Fto wildlife such as brown trout to
OL,18,Fkingfishers.
