OL,3,CWildlife left covered in diesel after
OL,4,Coil spill in chalk stream
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the agency said:
OL,7,F"On receiving reports of an oil spill
OL,8,Fon the River Wandle, officers were
OL,9,Fimmediately deployed to limit damage
OL,10,Fto the local environment and working
OL,11,Fwith the London Fire Brigade we have
OL,12,Fput in place measures to stop the
OL,13,Fleak."
OL,15,FIt is expected that the spill, thought
OL,16,Fto have come from a storage tank at a
OL,17,Fnearby bus depot, will affect the
OL,18,FWandle from Beddington to Wandsworth
OL,19,Fover the coming days.
