OL,3,CWildlife left covered in diesel after
OL,4,Coil spill in chalk stream
OL,6,FThe Environment Agency spokesperson
OL,7,Fadded: "We are currently gathering
OL,8,Fevidence and assessing the
OL,9,Fenvironmental impact for our
OL,10,Finvestigation, with the pollution
OL,11,Fsource suspected to be a bus depot
OL,12,Fstorage tank in Thornton Heath,
OL,13,FCroydon."
OL,15,FThe MP for Carshalton & Wallington,
OL,16,FBobby Dean, said residents had been
OL,17,Fcontacting him about the incident.
