OL,3,CWildlife left covered in diesel after
OL,4,Coil spill in chalk stream
OL,6,FIn a social media post on X, formerly
OL,7,FTwitter, the Lib Dem wrote: "Residents
OL,8,Fhave reported to me an environmental
OL,9,Fdisaster on the Wandle today.
OL,11,F"A major diesel spillage has left
OL,12,Fwildlife covered and caused untold
OL,13,Fdamage to the waterway.
OL,15,F"I'm in touch with the Environment
OL,16,FAgency and will make sure those
OL,17,Fresponsible are held to account."
