OL,3,CWildlife left covered in diesel after
OL,4,Coil spill in chalk stream
OL,6,FThe Wandle, which flows for nine miles
OL,7,Ffrom its source to the Thames, became
OL,8,Fheavily industrialised from the 17th
OL,9,Fto 19th centuries, suffering from
OL,10,Fsevere pollution.
OL,12,FFor many years the waterway was
OL,13,Fconsidered "ecologically dead",
OL,14,Faccording to the South East Rivers
OL,15,FTrust, but there has been a
OL,16,Fconsiderable effort to clean up the
OL,17,Friver and it is now a popular walking
OL,18,Ftrail.
