OL,3,CWildlife left covered in diesel after
OL,4,Coil spill in chalk stream
OL,6,FIt is home to brown trout, a key chalk
OL,7,Fstream species, which was re-
OL,8,Fintroduced to the river, while the
OL,9,FWandle and surrounding habitats
OL,10,Fsupport wildlife including
OL,11,Fkingfishers, damselflies and bats.
OL,13,FChalk streams are a globally rare
OL,14,Fhabitat, most of which are in England,
OL,15,Fand face a range of threats including
OL,16,Fclimate change, over abstraction of
OL,17,Fwater and pollution from sources
OL,18,Fincluding farming, urban run-off and
OL,19,Fsewage.
